d":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:14:24.000Z","msg":"是餓午<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a782099cda75fd2af78ab4e3e00a6034c6db71d","tid":2498193,"uid":111460,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會忘記昨晚.. <br />\n<br />\n我已經四日沒有東西落肚，昨晚終於忍不住，真的很肚餓，餓到連尊嚴也不顧... <br />\n沒有辦法，身上已無分文，屋企人又唔理，又找不到工作，連八達通的五十蚊按金也拿走了.. <br />\n<br />\n吃二手飯的感覺真的很難堪，昨晚在某屋村的大家樂，吃了別人剩下的飯餸，理不了別人的目光，一邊食眼淚俏俏的在眼角滴下......我是一個窮撚"},{"pid":"e08e38582c724dd8e3b9cd512bef23bc332b96fb","tid":2498193,"uid":321789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"大快人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859d69a38ea62934e6c770ee28f38cee8cda4110","tid":2498193,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94e4b36949beb7246f1c7a2fb085c88da95d1be7","tid":2498193,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:14:24.000Z","msg":"是餓午<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"是無午<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4793f15a7dc73b23960b1766bca41e9a0b9d66d9","tid":2498193,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a782099cda75fd2af78ab4e3e00a6034c6db71d","tid":2498193,"uid":111460,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會忘記昨晚.. <br />\n<br />\n我已經四日沒有東西落肚，昨晚終於忍不住，真的很肚餓，餓到連尊嚴也不顧... <br />\n沒有辦法，身上已無分文，屋企人又唔理，又找不到工作，連八達通的五十蚊按金也拿走了.. <br />\n<br />\n吃二手飯的感覺真的很難堪，昨晚在某屋村的大家樂，吃了別人剩下的飯餸，理不了別人的目光，一邊食眼淚俏俏的在眼角滴下......我是一個窮撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788307dfe222e8220d74131ccad7fd5071d09304","tid":2498193,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28d44b08f8f28f172282cdcdb419797c